This program uses openGL (graphics library) to provide some basic windowing capabilities. 
This means that you must install the OpenGL development libraries to be able to run this code.

     sudo apt-get update
     sudo apt-get upgrade
     sudo apt-get install binutils-gold
     sudo apt-get install libgl1-mesa-dev
     sudo apt-get install freeglut3 freeglut3-dev

Enter these sudo commands into your command line.
It will take a few minutes to install each. You must be connected to the Internet during the installation.
